You are here: Update Records Using External IDs in REST API

Update a record using the value of its external ID with the new updateOnly parameter in REST API. Previously, you could only upsert a record using its external ID.

Where: This change affects API version 61.0 and later.

How: Add the updateOnly parameter to a URL that executes an upsert operation or use URLs with the updateOnly parameter in composite REST API and composite graph REST API.
